sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as End-User Browser
    participant Axum as Axum API Server
    participant Registry as WebauthnRegistry (Moka)
    participant DB as Postgres (app_domains)
    participant Lib as webauthn-rs Builder

    Client->>Axum: POST /api/auth/passkey/register_options (Origin: dev.buildwithruud.com)
    Axum->>Registry: get_or_create("https://dev.buildwithruud.com")
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Registry: Cache Check
        Registry-->>Registry: Try lookup "https://dev.buildwithruud.com"
    end

    alt Cache Hit
        Registry-->>Axum: Return Arc<Webauthn>
    else Cache Miss (Concurrency Locked via try_get_with)
        Registry->>DB: Query app_domains (DomainName IN ["dev.buildwithruud.com", "buildwithruud.com"])
        
        alt Unauthorized Origin (Not in DB)
            DB-->>Registry: Return Empty/None
            Registry-->>Axum: Return Err("Unauthorized origin")
            Axum-->>Client: HTTP 403 Forbidden ("Network error")
        else Verified Tenant Origin
            DB-->>Registry: Return domain record
            
            Note over Registry: rp_id derivation via addr (eTLD+1)<br/>"dev.buildwithruud.com" -> "buildwithruud.com"
            
            Registry->>Lib: WebauthnBuilder::new("buildwithruud.com", "https://dev.buildwithruud.com")
            Lib-->>Registry: Build & Return Webauthn Instance
            Registry-->>Registry: Store Arc<Webauthn> in Moka Cache
            Registry-->>Axum: Return Arc<Webauthn>
        end
    end

    Axum->>Client: Return RegisterOptions JSON
